      <hr class="border-4 border-purple-600 cursor-pointer hover:border-yellow-500 duration-500">
      <p class="p-5 lg:text-3xl text-xl text-center">A free safespace to record precious and beloved <strong>experiences</strong>, <strong>interests</strong>, or anything else you <strong>desire.</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4 box-content w-2/5 bg-contain max-w-full h-auto border-yellow-600 border-4 rounded">
        <img src="../assets/images/pexels-tirachard-kumtanom-733857.jpg" 
          alt="An empty diary"
          class="transition-shadow ease-in-out duration-300 shadow-none hover:shadow-xl"
        >
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="flex justify-center items-center">
    <div class="box-content w-2/4 h-16 bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl flex justify-center relative -bottom-24">
      <p class="2xl:text-4xl xl:text-3xl lg:text-2xl md:text-xl text-center p-2">Join us and other users by signing up today!</p> 
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex justify-center relative -bottom-28 box-content">
    <ul class="steps mt-12">
      <li class="step step-primary text-yellow-50 text-2xl"><strong>Sign Up</strong></li>
      <li class="step step-primary text-yellow-50 text-2xl"><strong>Start Using Our App</strong></li>
      <li class="step text-yellow-50 text-2xl"><strong>That's It!</strong></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="container m-auto grid grid-cols-2 grid-rows-5 gap-6 relative -bottom-40">
      
