      <h1 class="text-4xl p-6">Features</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="box-content w-11/12 h-12 bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl flex relative place-self-center justify-center items-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl p-6">Benefits</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-benefits-cell">
      <h1 class="feature-benefits-text">Create new entries with a date and text.</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-benefits-cell">
      <h1 class="feature-benefits-text">Free to use, and easy to sign up!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-benefits-cell">
      <h1 class="feature-benefits-text">Show the date for each entry.</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-benefits-cell">
      <h1 class="feature-benefits-text">Set up goals to fulfill in the future or vent your anger out here!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-benefits-cell">
      <h1 class="feature-benefits-text">Show the most recent entries at the top first.</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-benefits-cell">
      <h1 class="feature-benefits-text">Calm your stress down by creating a diary entry. Putting things into words helps and can bring about more positive thought.</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-benefits-cell">
      <h1 class="feature-benefits-text">Attach pictures to go along with your entries.</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-benefits-cell">
      <h1 class="feature-benefits-text">Have a convoluted problem or issue that needs solving? Break down that problem into small steps to remember it more easily and to simplify things.</h1>
    </div>

  </div>

  <br>
  
  <div class="flex justify-center relative -bottom-56">
    <a href="/user/login">
      <button class="font-bold w-48 px-10 py-2 bg-cyan-500 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-cyan-600 hover:drop-shadow-md duration-300 ease-in text-lg"> Get started today! </button>
    </a>
  </div> 

  <br>
  <br>

  <div class="flex justify-center relative -bottom-44">
    <div class="box-content w-2/4 h-14 bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl flex justify-center relative -bottom-24 items-center">
      <p class="xl:text-4xl lg:ext-3xl text-xl text-center">Some thoughts from our users:</p> 
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container m-auto grid grid-cols-1 grid-rows-3 gap-y-8 relative justify-center -bottom-56">
    <div class="box-content w-5/6 h-24 bg-pink-200 bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl flex relative -bottom-24 items-center -right-14">
      <p class="2xl:text-3xl xl:text-2xl lg:ext-xl text-base text-center p-8"><strong>User 1</strong>: <q>Overall, this is a great app to vent out my frustrations. Also, the ability to add pictures is a nice touch!</q></p> 
    </div>

    <div class="box-content w-5/6 h-24 bg-pink-200 bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl flex relative justify-center -bottom-24 items-center -right-14">
      <p class="2xl:text-3xl xl:text-2xl lg:ext-xl text-base text-center p-8"><strong>User 2</strong>: <q>This app helps with my fuzzy memory. It makes it easy to organize my thoughts and I also love how the most recent entries show up first!</q></p> 
    </div>

    <div class="box-content w-5/6 h-24 bg-pink-200 bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl flex relative -bottom-24 items-center -right-14">
      <p class="2xl:text-3xl xl:text-2xl lg:ext-xl text-base text-center p-8"><strong>User 3</strong>: <q>Creating new entries can be done effortlessly. The user interface is aesthetically pleasing too!</q></p> 
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="box-content w-3/4 sm:h-20 h-28 bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl flex relative items-center lg:-right-48 md:-right-20 sm:-right-48 -right-16 -bottom-96 justify-center">
    <p class="xl:text-2xl lg:text-xl text-base p-8 text-center leading-loose">Have any <strong class="underline underline-offset-8">questions</strong>? Contact Us at: 
      <strong class="underline underline-offset-8 text-blue-600">someemail@gmail.com</strong> or through <strong class="underline underline-offset-8">(012)-3456-7891</strong>.</p> 
  </div>

  <div class="box-content w-1/2 h-16 bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl flex relative items-center FAQ-prompt justify-center">
    <p class="2xl:text-3xl xl:text-2xl lg:text-xl text-base p-8 text-center"> Frequently Asked Questions </p> 
  </div>

  <div class="grid justify-center gap-12 relative bottom-FAQs ">
    <div class="collapse border rounded-box border-base-300 collapse-plus bg-white opacity-90">
      <input type="checkbox"> 
      <div class="collapse-title text-2xl font-medium bg-plus">
        Just how private is my diary? Can other people see it?
      </div> 
      <div class="collapse-content text-xl"> 
        <hr class="border-2 border-purple-800 cursor-pointer hover:border-red-500 duration-500">
        <p class="p-3">No one else can see your diary. When you log in after creating an account, you get a diary that only you can see and you alone!</p>
      </div>
    </div> 

    <div class="collapse border rounded-box border-base-300 collapse-plus bg-white opacity-90">
      <input type="checkbox"> 
      <div class="collapse-title text-2xl font-medium">
        How much do I need to pay to get access to my own online diary?
      </div> 
      <div class="collapse-content text-xl"> 
        <hr class="border-2 border-purple-800 cursor-pointer hover:border-red-500 duration-500">
        <p class="p-3">Nothing at all! There are no payments required or subscriptions. It is completely free and all you have to do is sign up.</p>
      </div>
    </div> 

    <div class="collapse border rounded-box border-base-300 collapse-plus bg-white opacity-90">
      <input type="checkbox"> 
      <div class="collapse-title text-2xl font-medium">
        Why should I use this application instead of just buying a traditional diary and a pencil to record my experiences?
      </div> 
      <div class="collapse-content text-xl"> 
        <hr class="border-2 border-purple-800 cursor-pointer hover:border-red-500 duration-500">
        <p class="p-3">You are capable of inserting photos which can give entries more depth and you can add emojis. Also, unlike a physical diary, this app is completely free.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex relative justify-center make-it-happen-image">
    <div class="mb-4 box-content h-1/3 w-1/3 bg-contain border-yellow-600 border-4 rounded">
        <img class ="h-auto transition-shadow ease-in-out duration-300 shadow-none hover:shadow-xl" 
        src="../assets/images/pexels-bich-tran-669986.jpg" 
        alt="A Diary"
        />
